  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">RESCUING OF 100 STIGMATIZED  CHILDREN IN NIGERIA</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">In The Niger Delta region of Nigeria, thousands of children have been labeled as witches and wizards, tortured, and abandoned by their families and some religious preachers. The children bear scars and wounds of horrendous abuse and torture. Some of the children have been chained in the dark rooms, toilets, and prayer houses for months before being forced to the streets; and we want to rescue them.</narrative>
  </description>
